{
  "id": "69f991718e35edcb2624baab",
  "title": "麦茶の容器",
  "created": 1777963377,
  "updated": 1777963389,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f991718e35edcb2624baab",
      "text": "麦茶の容器",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03ab",
      "text": "from [2026/05/05]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917800000000002c03bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963385,
      "updated": 1777963385
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03ac",
      "text": "[麦茶]の容器[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963389
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03ad",
      "text": "\t以前は口が丸いビン製を使ってた",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03ae",
      "text": "\t\t中の掃除が面倒くさいのがネックだった",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03af",
      "text": "\t\t\t手首が入らないから食器のように洗えない",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b0",
      "text": "\t\t\tブラシのようなもので洗ってた",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b1",
      "text": "\t去年は横長のドリンクサーバーみたいなのを使ってた",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b2",
      "text": "\t\thttps://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B0D2NPN3ZC?th=1 こんなの",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b3",
      "text": "\t\tケースは洗いやすくなった",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b4",
      "text": "\t\t逆にデメリットも多数",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b5",
      "text": "\t\t\t液漏れする",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b6",
      "text": "\t\t\t出し入れ時に安定せずに零しがち",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b7",
      "text": "\t\t\t栓の部分が複数パーツ構成で、その中を洗うとなるとパーツを分解したり組み立てたり、という面倒臭さがあった",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b8",
      "text": "\t今年は「手首が入るぐらい口の大きいもの」を買ってみた",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9917100000000002c03b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1777963377,
      "updated": 1777963377
